data.description: Discover your dream home in Coral Springs, FL! This stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo offers a recently renovated kitchen, new air conditioner, and a prime location. With top-rated schools and a vibrant community, you'll enjoy beautiful parks, shopping centers, and dining options. The community is known for its friendly atmosphere and welcoming spirit, making it the perfect place to call home.   Financing is available with only 10% down.  Don't miss your chance to experience the best of Florida living in this amazing apartment. Schedule a tour today!
